  "character_description": "Mr Spooky is a comedy-horror vampire fighter with pale face paint, dark eye makeup, fake blood at the mouth, messy short black hair, a fitted black lace-up shirt, black pants, black gloves, black boots, and an oversized shiny red satin cape with black lining. He fights with overacted fright poses, cape flourishes, awkward low sweeps, and silly haunted-showmanship energy.\nSilhouette: slim theatrical vampire performer, hunched and springy, dominated by the wide red cape.\nClothing: fitted black shirt with lace-up collar, black pants, black gloves, black boots, red satin cape with black lining.\nHair: short messy dark hair.\nAccessories: oversized red cape and a small rubber bat projectile.\nAttitude: goofy spooky showman, fake-fright panic, melodramatic vampire flourish.\nDistinctive traits: white face makeup, blood at the mouth, cape spread poses, comedy-horror bat release.",
